+- `library/meta/obstruction-screening/record-when-a-candidate-claim-is-only-a-proxy-level-insertion-line.md`
+
+## Constraints
+
+- Do not rerun packet search.
+- Do not change the carried-friendly witnesses or hostile comparator.
+- Do not treat the Step-4 or Step-5 dossier itself as a completed theorem or
+  counterexample result.
